  "artwork_generated_url": "",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.02,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.02,
      "end": 34.26,
      "text": "날이면 날마다 찾게 되는 영화 맛집"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.26,
      "end": 36.28,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 36.28,
      "end": 38.56,
      "text": "6월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.56,
      "end": 43.34,
      "text": "천재 발명가들을 둘러싼 역사적인 전류전쟁 이야기"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.34,
      "end": 45.14,
      "text": "The current war"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.14,
      "end": 46.82,
      "text": "와, hi, 크리스"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.82,
      "end": 48.14,
      "text": "Hello, Laura, good morning"
    },
    {
      "start": 48.14,
      "end": 49.92,
      "text": "Yeah, how are you doing?"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.16,
      "end": 52.64,
      "text": "I'm doing okay, so-so"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.64,
      "end": 53.04,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.04,
      "end": 53.96,
      "text": "Not bad"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.96,
      "end": 54.36,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.36,
      "end": 59.2,
      "text": "우리 영화가 거의 끝나가는 시점이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.2,
      "end": 60.6,
      "text": "Yeah, almost over"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.6,
      "end": 62.64,
      "text": "Why do you sound sad?"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.64,
      "end": 66.94,
      "text": "과연 전류전쟁의 승자가 누가 될 것인가"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.94,
      "end": 69.44,
      "text": "점점 더 궁금해지는데요"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.44,
      "end": 70.8,
      "text": "The suspense is building"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.8,
      "end": 73.32,
      "text": "I cannot wait to find out"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.32,
      "end": 73.88,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 73.88,
      "end": 77.3,
      "text": "사실 다 알지만 아직까지는 비밀을 린 걸로"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.3,
      "end": 78.42,
      "text": "Yeah, 우리 봤으니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.42,
      "end": 79.02,
      "text": "그러게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.02,
      "end": 79.8,
      "text": "그 전에"
    },
    {
      "start": 79.8,
      "end": 81.2,
      "text": "Whose side were you on?"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.32,
      "end": 82.62,
      "text": "Edison versus Tesla"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.62,
      "end": 85.2,
      "text": "Well, of course, naturally, at first"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.2,
      "end": 87.54,
      "text": "Edison is the main character"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.54,
      "end": 87.82,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 87.82,
      "end": 88.84,
      "text": "The star of the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.84,
      "end": 91.9,
      "text": "So, naturally, I was rooting for Edison"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.9,
      "end": 92.44,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.44,
      "end": 93.1,
      "text": "Go, Edison"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.1,
      "end": 93.14,
      "text": "Go, Edison!"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.74,
      "end": 95.84,
      "text": "And his wife died"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.84,
      "end": 98.96,
      "text": "He was struggling with his family"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.96,
      "end": 100.48,
      "text": "So, I felt for him"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.48,
      "end": 101.98,
      "text": "I wanted him to win"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.98,
      "end": 103.04,
      "text": "그렇구나"
    },
    {
      "start": 103.04,
      "end": 105.6,
      "text": "But going on in the movie, I kind of changed that"
    },
    {
      "start": 105.6,
      "end": 107.94,
      "text": "I kind of, I like the underdog"
    },
    {
      "start": 107.94,
      "end": 110.36,
      "text": "I always have supported the underdog"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.36,
      "end": 110.64,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 110.64,
      "end": 111.72,
      "text": "In sports, too"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.72,
      "end": 112.06,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.06,
      "end": 116.2,
      "text": "I root for the team that nobody thinks is going to win"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.2,
      "end": 118.92,
      "text": "So, I started supporting Tesla"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.92,
      "end": 119.88,
      "text": "그렇군요"
    },
    {
      "start": 119.88,
      "end": 120.96,
      "text": "I felt bad for him"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.96,
      "end": 123.0,
      "text": "He got ripped off by Edison"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.0,
      "end": 123.66,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.66,
      "end": 124.7,
      "text": "He was betrayed"
    },
    {
      "start": 124.7,
      "end": 127.38,
      "text": "And he is a smart guy"
    },
    {
      "start": 127.38,
      "end": 128.22,
      "text": "With passion"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.22,
      "end": 131.16,
      "text": "그래요, 처음에는 Edison 응원했지만"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.16,
      "end": 134.56,
      "text": "점차적으로 우리 테슬라를 응원하게 되셨다고 하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 134.56,
      "end": 136.02,
      "text": "제 생각에는 원래"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.02,
      "end": 138.96,
      "text": "캘리포니아 부심이 있다 보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 138.96,
      "end": 139.66,
      "text": "우리 크리스가"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.66,
      "end": 141.66,
      "text": "당연히 저는"
    },
    {
      "start": 141.66,
      "end": 142.32,
      "text": "아, 그거 빠트렸다니"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.32,
      "end": 143.5,
      "text": "You were rooting for Tesla"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.5,
      "end": 144.32,
      "text": "할 줄 알았어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.32,
      "end": 145.84,
      "text": "우리 고향 회사"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.84,
      "end": 146.76,
      "text": "Cool"
    },
    {
      "start": 146.76,
      "end": 148.4,
      "text": "테슬라"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.4,
      "end": 154.2,
      "text": "저는 베네딕트 컴버베치"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.2,
      "end": 155.36,
      "text": "이름이 너무 헷갈렸어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.36,
      "end": 156.58,
      "text": "웨스틴하우스"
    },
    {
      "start": 156.58,
      "end": 158.7,
      "text": "베네딕트 컴버베치"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.7,
      "end": 163.4,
      "text": "그러니까 에디슨의 역할을 맡은 베네딕트 컴버베치에 그냥 몰입을"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.4,
      "end": 164.66,
      "text": "아, you just like the actor"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.66,
      "end": 164.7,
      "text": "아, you just like the actor"
    },
    {
      "start": 164.7,
      "end": 166.56,
      "text": "아, you just like the 남자"
    },
    {
      "start": 166.56,
      "end": 168.66,
      "text": "남자는 무슨"
    },
    {
      "start": 168.66,
      "end": 169.5,
      "text": "The guy"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.5,
      "end": 173.04,
      "text": "오이씨께 몰입을 계속 했었을 뿐이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 173.04,
      "end": 174.6,
      "text": "역사적으로 좀 분석하세요"
    },
    {
      "start": 174.6,
      "end": 175.7,
      "text": "그러게 말입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.7,
      "end": 177.38,
      "text": "중도를 지켜야죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.38,
      "end": 179.74,
      "text": "자, 결과적으로는 어때요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.98,
      "end": 186.22,
      "text": "웨스틴하우스와 테슬라하고 같이 합력해서 이기게 되는 그런 상황이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.22,
      "end": 186.76,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.76,
      "end": 191.52,
      "text": "그런데 에디슨은 전혀 패배자라는 생각은 들지 않게 해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.52,
      "end": 193.5,
      "text": "왜냐하면 이미 우리가 나눴던 것처럼"
    },
    {
      "start": 193.5,
      "end": 196.6,
      "text": "에디슨 has more than thousands of patents"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.6,
      "end": 198.34,
      "text": "Sure, over a thousand patents"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.34,
      "end": 198.76,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.76,
      "end": 200.46,
      "text": "That's more than his competitors"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.46,
      "end": 200.96,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.96,
      "end": 202.3,
      "text": "And he's a celebrity"
    },
    {
      "start": 202.3,
      "end": 203.78,
      "text": "Everybody likes him"
    },
    {
      "start": 203.78,
      "end": 205.16,
      "text": "They ask for his autograph"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.16,
      "end": 206.96,
      "text": "They want to take pictures with him"
    },
    {
      "start": 206.96,
      "end": 208.22,
      "text": "Everybody loves 에디슨"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.22,
      "end": 210.56,
      "text": "Yeah, so in the last scene of the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.56,
      "end": 212.56,
      "text": "영화의 거의 끝장면에서는"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.56,
      "end": 215.92,
      "text": "There was an invention that influenced the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 215.92,
      "end": 218.32,
      "text": "영화에 뭔가 관련되는"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.32,
      "end": 221.26,
      "text": "그의 발명품이 또 하나가 딱 등장하게 되는"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.26,
      "end": 222.34,
      "text": "기억이 납니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.34,
      "end": 223.66,
      "text": "Really? What was that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 224.85,
      "end": 225.81,
      "text": "슬슬 알아볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.81,
      "end": 227.89,
      "text": "자, 오늘 장면 일단 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.89,
      "end": 231.19,
      "text": "I have books so full of ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 231.19,
      "end": 233.73,
      "text": "It would take me more than 12 lifetimes to execute"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.73,
      "end": 236.45,
      "text": "So let the man have his fair and waterfall"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.45,
      "end": 237.67,
      "text": "Well, for its worth"
    },
    {
      "start": 237.67,
      "end": 240.87,
      "text": "Much rather to work for you than 웨스틴하우스 any day"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.87,
      "end": 241.91,
      "text": "Why is that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 242.31,
      "end": 243.73,
      "text": "Well, I wouldn't have had as much fun, would I?"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.73,
      "end": 248.67,
      "text": "와, 진짜 이 웨스틴하우스하고 테슬라가 힘을 합하니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.67,
      "end": 250.35,
      "text": "They became invincible"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.35,
      "end": 251.71,
      "text": "Yes"
    },
    {
      "start": 251.71,
      "end": 253.97,
      "text": "완전 천하무적 탄생"
    },
    {
      "start": 253.97,
      "end": 254.77,
      "text": "Dream team"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.77,
      "end": 255.29,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.29,
      "end": 256.63,
      "text": "They beat Mr. 에디슨"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.63,
      "end": 259.91,
      "text": "그리고 이제 에디슨이 전류전쟁에서 패하게 되잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.91,
      "end": 262.33,
      "text": "그러다가 이제 회사에서 쫓겨나게 되고"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.33,
      "end": 265.59,
      "text": "How was the name of his company changed?"
    },
    {
      "start": 265.59,
      "end": 267.95,
      "text": "So it changed from Edison Electric"
    },
    {
      "start": 267.95,
      "end": 271.13,
      "text": "into the very, very famous company"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.13,
      "end": 273.39,
      "text": "that is still operating today"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.39,
      "end": 274.71,
      "text": "Very successfully"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.71,
      "end": 276.63,
      "text": "General Electric"
    },
    {
      "start": 276.63,
      "end": 278.51,
      "text": "A.K.A. GE"
    },
    {
      "start": 278.51,
      "end": 281.15,
      "text": "오, 원래는 에디슨 일렉트릭이었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.15,
      "end": 286.11,
      "text": "이제 General Electric이라는 회사로 이름을 바꾸게 되는 거죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 286.11,
      "end": 287.41,
      "text": "Yeah, Mr. J.P. Morgan"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.41,
      "end": 289.81,
      "text": "The big tycoon, the big banker"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.81,
      "end": 292.57,
      "text": "merges his Edison's company"
    },
    {
      "start": 292.57,
      "end": 294.31,
      "text": "into General Electric"
    },
    {
      "start": 294.31,
      "end": 299.47,
      "text": "오, 그리고 그 사무엘 인솔의 목소리가 좀 전에 들렸잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.47,
      "end": 303.51,
      "text": "근데 이 사람이 에디슨을 대신해서 입찰을 했잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.51,
      "end": 304.95,
      "text": "에디슨's right-hand man"
    },
    {
      "start": 304.95,
      "end": 306.89,
      "text": "오, 근데 나름 잘했다고 생각했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.89,
      "end": 309.25,
      "text": "웨스틴하우스가 이기게 되었죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.25,
      "end": 311.69,
      "text": "웨스틴하우스 was very, did you see the way?"
    },
    {
      "start": 311.93,
      "end": 315.13,
      "text": "He persuaded the people to vote for him"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.13,
      "end": 315.47,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 315.47,
      "end": 318.19,
      "text": "He was very clever, very business-like"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.19,
      "end": 318.55,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 318.55,
      "end": 319.09,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 319.09,
      "end": 320.57,
      "text": "So he was successful"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.57,
      "end": 322.05,
      "text": "He came out on top"
    },
    {
      "start": 322.05,
      "end": 325.35,
      "text": "자, 어떤 표현이 들렸는지 살펴볼게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 325.35,
      "end": 327.97,
      "text": "So full of ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 327.97,
      "end": 330.21,
      "text": "Full of ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 330.21,
      "end": 332.35,
      "text": "라는 것도 아이디어가 넘쳐나는 건데"
    },
    {
      "start": 332.35,
      "end": 334.17,
      "text": "So full of ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 334.17,
      "end": 335.51,
      "text": "I'm so full of ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 335.51,
      "end": 338.85,
      "text": "아이디어가 엄청나게 넘쳐나는 이라는 의미입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 338.85,
      "end": 341.17,
      "text": "Yeah, inventors should be full of ideas"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.17,
      "end": 341.55,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 341.55,
      "end": 343.21,
      "text": "Execute"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.21,
      "end": 346.77,
      "text": "Execute라는 단어는 무서운 단어이기도 하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 346.77,
      "end": 348.29,
      "text": "It could be a very scary thing"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.29,
      "end": 348.51,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 348.51,
      "end": 349.51,
      "text": "Or a good thing"
    },
    {
      "start": 349.51,
      "end": 353.77,
      "text": "처형하다라는 그런 부정적인 의미에서도 쓰일 수가 있을 뿐더러"
    },
    {
      "start": 353.77,
      "end": 358.13,
